{"type": "article", "id": 5780, "title": "FUDO & KKINI 碗筷系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-02T07:40:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233951rO0ZwYf4P12l3tov.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tFUDO 与 KKINI 碗筷系列为 JIA Inc. 品家家品去年的作品，邀请日本建筑大师黑川雅之 (MasayukiKurokawa)与韩国新锐设计师宋承容(Seung Yong Song)，展现东方国度对“家”的记忆创作，让日常普通的食器成为艺术家、设计师们创作的载体，让使用者感受大地藏无尽的丰硕与富饶，体会人生的百般况味。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233950OMntS93UIePZkmXG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233950LE71G3AIu96zZdcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233950IHaDQBTzjYSkiwxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}